{
	"id": "a2-unit-08",
	"cefrLevel": "A2",
	"order": 8,
	"title": "Donner son opinion — Giving opinions",
	"objective": "Express and justify simple opinions (A2: can give and explain opinions on familiar topics).",
	"bridge": {
		"title": "Bridge from Hindi / English: « je pense que … » + a reason with « parce que »",
		"body": "Open an opinion with **je pense que** / **je crois que** / **à mon avis**, then a full sentence: *Je pense que ce film est intéressant.* Give a reason with **parce que** (because) and link ideas with **mais** (but), **donc** (so), **aussi** (also). It mirrors English “I think that …” and Hindi मुझे लगता है कि … — same shape, just learn the connectors."
	},
	"cards": [
